data.name: SqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO TblReport(AreaId, EventDate, EventTime, EventYYMM, CutOffRepairTime, CutoffGroupId, PrimaryReasonId) VALUES (@AreaId, @EventDate, @EventTime, @EventYYMM, @CutOffRepairTime, @CutoffGroupId, @PrimaryReasonId)

data.name: SqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE TblReport SET AreaId = @AreaId, EventDate = @EventDate, EventTime = @EventTime, EventYYMM = @EventYYMM, CutOffRepairTime = @CutOffRepairTime, CutoffGroupId = @CutoffGroupId, PrimaryReasonId = @PrimaryReasonId WHERE (RepId = @Original_RepId)
